tiers.ability_description: Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever First Order allies Stun an enemy, they gain Speed Up and Offense Up for 2 turns and inflict Expose for 2 turns at the end of that turn, which can't be evaded.
Whenever another ally attacks during General Hux's turn, General Hux and that ally gain 25% Turn Meter (limit once per turn).
Whenever Dark Side allies use a Basic ability, they gain Critical Chance Up, Critical Damage Up, and Offense Up for 2 turns.
Whenever a First Order ally has full Health and Protection at the start of their turn, they deal +100% more Damage on their turn.

Whenever Supreme Leader Kylo Ren has 100 or more stacks of Siphon, he ignores Stealth and Taunt during his turn. For every 20 stacks of Siphon he has, First Order allies gain 10% Defense and 10% Health Steal (stacking, max 200%) until the end of the encounter.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.

Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User critically hits an enemy, dispel all debuffs on themself and gain 5% Turn Meter. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability against an enemy with at least 3 debuffs, reduce that enemy's Max Health by 5%. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability when they have at least 3 buffs that can be dispelled, gain 5% Max Health.

Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker damages an enemy with a Special ability and the enemy doesn't have Armor Shred, inflict Armor Shred on them for the rest of the battle. Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker uses a Basic ability and damages an enemy with Armor Shred, inflict Expose for 2 turns, which can't be resisted, and Commander Luke Skywalker gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
At the start of the encounter, the weakest ally gains 20% Turn Meter for every Light Side ally.
The first time each Unaligned Force User ally falls below 50% Health they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn and gain Health Steal Up for 2 turns.
The first time each turn Rey gains Ultimate Charge, they gain an additional 6% Ultimate Charge.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain Tenacity Up, they gain Protection Up (10%, stacking) for 2 turns.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.
Light Side allies start the battle with +25% Turn Meter.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever a Attacker ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Marked, inflict Marked for 1 turn on the target enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
At the start of each turn, if non-Galactic Legend Tank allies have 50% or more Turn Meter, damage they receive is reduced by 75% until the end of the turn.

Each time Poggle the Lesser inflicts Ability Block, he also inflicts Burning for 2 turns on the target enemy, Poggle the Lesser gains 10% Turn Meter, and all allies gain 20% Offense (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever IG-86 critically hits an enemy, IG-86 gains Damage Immunity for 1 turn, 25% Turn Meter, and inflicts Deathmark on the target enemy for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted. If the enemy was already Deathmarked, IG-86 gains Protection Up (50%, stacking), Retribution, and Speed Up for 2 turns.

If HK-47 is in the Leader slot, whenever an ally damages an enemy with Ability Block or Fear, IG-88 assists, Shocks that enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted, and inflicts them with Torture for 1 turn, which can't be copied, dispelled, evaded, or resisted, and all allies gain Offense Up for 2 turns.

At the start of each encounter, Poe inflicts Fear on all enemies, which can't be copied, dispelled, evaded, prevented, or resisted, and Exposes them for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever Taunt expires on Poe, all enemies are inflicted with Fear for 1 turn, which can't be copied or dispelled, and all allies gain 20% Turn Meter. Whenever Poe Dameron is critically hit while Taunting, he gains Protection Up (50%) for 1 turn. Whenever a buff expires on another ally, Poe Taunts for 1 turn.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever a Attacker ally defeats an enemy, they take a bonus turn.

At the start of each encounter, Dengar inflicts Doubt on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded, dispelled, or resisted.

Whenever an enemy evades Dengar's attack or resists a debuff, all enemies are inflicted with a stack of Damage Over Time and Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Zam always critically hits if able. The first time Zam is defeated while there are any active allies, Zam revives with 100% Health and Stealths for 3 turns.

Whenever Zam inflicts an enemy with Thermal Detonators, she gains 10% Defense and Offense (stacking) for the rest of the encounter, and there is a 50% chance to inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns.
